data.description: This spacious open layout 4 large bed room 3 full bath plus a bonus room and 3 car a garage home is ready to be yours! Come experience all of the great amenities of Waters Edge! The large kitchen features a brand new stove and refrigerator, 42" wood cabinets, corian counter tops, a breakfast bar and plenty of storage space including a pantry and a large eat in area for every day use. Enjoy the separate dining room for all of the big family holidays. There is room for the whole family to relax with the separate living room and family room layout. The master bed room has a huge walk in closet. The master bath has his and her sinks, a large walk in shower and a tub! The common areas share beautiful large ceramic tile. This community has so much to offer including a beautiful club house, pool, tennis courts, boat ramp, lake, play grounds and so much more!
